   new testament traditions    thumb|left|james tissot - healing of the lepers at capernaum ( guérison des lépreux à capernaum ) - brooklyn museum   the town is cited in all four gospels ( matthew 4:13,8:5,11:23,17:24 , mark 1:21,2:1,9:33 , luke 4:23,31,7:1,10:15 , john 2:12,4:46,6:17,24,59 ) where it was reported to have been near the hometown of the apostles simon peter , andrew , james and john , as well as the tax collector matthew .

